snippet.title: Floor 13: Deep State | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Learn more: https://www.humblegames.com/floor13/

In Floor 13, a Dynamically Generated, Document-Driven Dystopia, you use the power of the deep state to deal with truth.

Fake news, illegal surveillance, extraordinary rendition, or assassination. It doesn’t matter how — all you need to do is sign the order.

Follow Humble Games: 
TW: https://bit.ly/HumbleGames_TW
